what are your preferences are,

00:54:45.040 --> 00:54:49.160
whom would you like to get married,
if there is somebody in your mind

00:54:49.160 --> 00:54:52.120
you better act.

00:54:52.120 --> 00:54:58.748
And also after consulting that person.
(Laughter)

00:54:58.747 --> 00:55:03.359
Otherwise it would&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:55:03.360 --> 00:55:10.880
be very embarrassing.
(Laughter)

00:55:10.880 --> 00:55:14.680
And clearly you must state
what sort of person you want to marry

00:55:14.680 --> 00:55:21.473
and also clearly about yourself, you see
that what you are doing,

00:55:21.473 --> 00:55:26.920
if you are capable or earning or not,
capable of supporting your wife or not,

00:55:26.920 --> 00:55:33.120
such a thing, you must write so that –
or if wife is there she should also write,

00:55:33.120 --> 00:55:40.200
if she can help her husband
in any material area or anything,

00:55:40.200 --> 00:55:44.720
so you must clearly write in the form,
it’s all there, nothing to hide.

00:55:44.720 --> 00:55:48.240
Nothing to say something, which is not there.

00:55:48.240 --> 00:55:51.400
Because these things can be quite misleading,
all right?

00:55:51.400 --> 00:55:55.520
And no leader is going to put anything
absurd now because we have had

00:55:55.520 --> 00:55:58.600
funny experiences before.

00:55:58.600 --> 00:56:04.200
But there is one thing – getting into
Sahaja Yoga marriage is very different

00:56:04.200 --> 00:56:06.320
from any other marriage.

00:56:06.320 --> 00:56:11.111
Of course, Sahaja Yoga has got
all the facilities for divorce also.

00:56:11.111 --> 00:56:14.600
There is no – that we don’t say
that you cannot divorce.

00:56:14.600 --> 00:56:17.920
You can divorce,
but under certain circumstances.

00:56:17.920 --> 00:56:22.160
But after marriage some of the people
just get lost.

00:56:22.160 --> 00:56:26.560
And this is something – the worst type
of thing that can happen to you.

00:56:26.560 --> 00:56:29.600
They get into their honeymoon mood
and I don’t know what they get into –

00:56:29.600 --> 00:56:36.280
all their ideas, romantic ideas come back,
they were just lost with that.

00:56:36.280 --> 00:56:39.800
You are marrying here for Sahaja Yoga.

00:56:39.800 --> 00:56:41.720
That’s the main thing to remember.

00:56:41.720 --> 00:56:43.320
And don’t forget.

00:56:43.320 --> 00:56:47.800
Because this has been seen with some
percentage of them, not with all that,

00:56:47.800 --> 00:56:49.280
they get lost.

00:56:49.280 --> 00:56:53.280
They start dominating each other,
fighting with each other,

00:56:53.960 --> 00:56:59.280
trying to be funny
and some of them are shocked, shocked.

00:56:59.280 --> 00:57:04.200
And some have left Sahaja Yoga
because of their marriages.

00:57:04.200 --> 00:57:08.840
And another if you have any –
like if you have children

00:57:08.840 --> 00:57:15.800
and if there is a case going on –
better not marry. Forget about it.

00:57:15.800 --> 00:57:19.000
If you are free, absolutely free
there is no problem of that kind

00:57:19.000 --> 00:57:20.956
then you better marry.

00:57:20.956 --> 00:57:24.520
But if you have a problem
that another person going to sue you

00:57:24.520 --> 00:57:29.080
and do all these things, it’s absurd.
It’s a very common thing.

00:57:29.080 --> 00:57:33.800
So, also I would say last thing that
if you have such problems of your children

00:57:33.800 --> 00:57:38.760
are with somebody else,
you have to forget about the children

00:57:38.760 --> 00:57:44.473
If you have the children with you
then if you [have that lady, who ??]

00:57:44.473 --> 00:57:50.720
always trouble us, talk about Sahaja Yoga,
do this do that.

00:57:50.720 --> 00:57:54.320
So, in Sahaja Yoga, you see,
it is not practical.

00:57:54.320 --> 00:57:56.360
It’s not practical I have seen.

00:57:56.360 --> 00:58:03.077
If you want to have the children or anything
then the husband if he is against Sahaja Yoga

00:58:03.077 --> 00:58:06.600
he may say that, “All right,
you can be a Sahaja Yogini

00:58:06.600 --> 00:58:09.680
but I will not allow our children to be in it.”
And he won’t like it.

00:58:09.680 --> 00:58:14.520
So why don’t have a [liability ?]
and see the child yourself and meet the child.

00:58:14.520 --> 00:58:20.680
You don’t have a liability
of children on yourself.

00:58:20.680 --> 00:58:25.320
In Sahaja Yoga also there are people
who have misbehaved

00:58:25.320 --> 00:58:30.280
who have been with Me for ages –
I’ve treated them just like My own children.

00:58:30.280 --> 00:58:34.960
I forgive them because they couldn’t [go on ?].

00:58:34.960 --> 00:58:39.320
So this kind of attachment is also is not good
which creates problems for your ascent.

00:58:39.320 --> 00:58:42.840
You are in Sahaja Yoga for your ascent.
Your marriage is for your ascent.

00:58:42.840 --> 00:58:44.680
Your children are for your ascent.

00:58:44.680 --> 00:58:50.800
Anybody which creates a problem or hurdles
for your ascent you should try to forget it

00:58:50.800 --> 00:58:52.160
because God knows how many times&nbsp;

00:58:52.160 --> 00:58:54.920
you have been married in&nbsp;
your last lives? (Laughter)

00:58:54.920 --> 00:58:59.000
And how many children you have had.
So all these attachments are superficial.

00:58:59.000 --> 00:59:03.200
You are special people
as far as Sahaja Yoga is concerned.

00:59:03.200 --> 00:59:08.200
So you’ll give it a thought that you are
not going to divorce next day, it’s not good.

00:59:08.200 --> 00:59:09.640
I don’t like it.

00:59:09.640 --> 00:59:11.600
If you don’t want to marry – don’t marry.

00:59:11.600 --> 00:59:15.800
If you want to marry a person
there’s one month choice – you can find out.

00:59:15.800 --> 00:59:18.280
Like somebody – decide for yourself.

00:59:18.280 --> 00:59:22.480
You may not fall into love, may not,
that’s also another thing I don’t know,

00:59:22.480 --> 00:59:24.640
what to fall into love.

00:59:24.640 --> 00:59:27.840
That kind of thing may not be
and it is not necessary

00:59:27.840 --> 00:59:37.440
because if you fall into love
also rise into divorces. (Laughter)

00:59:37.440 --> 00:59:41.880
So best thing is not to fall into love
and not to rise into divorces,

00:59:41.880 --> 00:59:44.720
but have a balanced idea about marriage.

00:59:44.720 --> 00:59:50.226
See, marriage, it cannot be decided
like the way you have Romeo and Juliet

00:59:50.226 --> 00:59:51.360
or something, nothing of that kind.

00:59:51.360 --> 00:59:56.040
Life is practical, you see, it’s practical life,
your feet should be on the ground,

00:59:56.040 --> 01:00:00.760
you see, absolutely on the ground.
So you won’t lose your balance.

01:00:00.760 --> 01:00:03.920
So if you understand that point
then marriage will be successful.

01:00:03.920 --> 01:00:09.520
But if you try to think of a romanticism
and all that – it just fails.

01:00:09.520 --> 01:00:14.320
Of course at the same time I would say
it is not ascetism of any kind at all

01:00:14.320 --> 01:00:21.560
but you lead a nice, friendly married life,
in a very friendly manner in every way,

01:00:21.560 --> 01:00:23.760
decent and decorous.

01:00:23.760 --> 01:00:28.320
But you do not become sort of over romantic
so that another person runs away

01:00:28.320 --> 01:00:32.280
with your romanticism.

01:00:32.280 --> 01:00:34.480
I’ve told many a times about it.

01:00:34.480 --> 01:00:38.600
That you have all the freedom to choose
which ever person you like

01:00:38.600 --> 01:00:41.320
and you can always say,
“No, Mother I don’t want to [belong ?].”

01:00:41.320 --> 01:00:44.680
You have all the freedom everything.

01:00:44.680 --> 01:00:47.600
I never force you to do anything
even in Sahaja Yoga.

01:00:47.600 --> 01:00:50.160
If you want to stay in Sahaja Yoga
you stay all right –

01:00:50.160 --> 01:00:52.080
if you don’t want to stay you can go.

01:00:52.080 --> 01:00:56.920
So there’s no compulsion of any kind
in Sahaja Yoga.

01:00:56.920 --> 01:01:02.000
If you don’t want to get married – all right,
if you want to get married – all right.

01:01:02.000 --> 01:01:06.440
So it is your Spirit which has to guide you.
I am not going to say anything.

01:01:06.440 --> 01:01:09.780
I’ve never even said that,
“Give up drugs, alcohol – anything.”

01:01:09.780 --> 01:01:11.880
It just works automatically.

01:01:11.880 --> 01:01:18.080
So if you want to develop a state
of your Spirit you have to listen to it

01:01:18.080 --> 01:01:21.160
and it will be seen in your own life
that you are wise.

01:01:21.160 --> 01:01:23.160
You must know how to handle your wife,&nbsp;

01:01:23.160 --> 01:01:29.000
how to handle yourself, handle&nbsp;
your tempers and things.

01:01:29.000 --> 01:01:32.720
And that’s one of the tests –
that’s the test in Sahaja Yoga.

01:01:32.720 --> 01:01:40.280
So I hope marriage is not the priority,
not the prior thing. It is not that.

01:01:40.280 --> 01:01:45.160
It is supportive, it is not the prior.
What is prior is Kundalini.

01:01:45.160 --> 01:01:54.200
Standing on that primordial principle
and you have to adjust yourself to that principle

01:01:54.200 --> 01:01:58.080
and with that you can see
that others can be also adjusted.

01:01:58.080 --> 01:02:03.240
We have ways and methods, silent methods
of improving others – not arguments,

01:02:03.240 --> 01:02:08.520
not talking, not saying harsh things, no,
but silent ways of doing things.

01:02:08.520 --> 01:02:11.400
And it works.

01:02:11.400 --> 01:02:17.200
Of course, if somebody is horrible – like that
I am not going to in any way,

01:02:17.200 --> 01:02:21.140
any way ask him to continue with that person,
all right finish it.

01:02:21.140 --> 01:02:24.400
But you must know when to finish it.

01:02:24.400 --> 01:02:27.560
I mean it’s very surprising that people&nbsp;

01:02:27.560 --> 01:02:30.960
do not want to finish off&nbsp;
with the problems they face,

01:02:30.960 --> 01:02:33.200
because of their children,&nbsp;
because of their husbands,&nbsp;

01:02:33.200 --> 01:02:34.720
this, that. But they are very anxious

01:02:34.720 --> 01:02:39.200
to have a divorce, it’s very surprising.

01:02:39.200 --> 01:02:45.800
It has become like a market, marketing.
It’s so much in the atmosphere –

01:02:45.800 --> 01:02:48.920
you must divorce, you must divorce.

01:02:48.920 --> 01:02:52.120
In India you don’t have anybody
falling into love, I mean,

01:02:52.120 --> 01:02:55.000
we don’t know that part
but we have very good marriages

01:02:55.000 --> 01:02:57.880
and we have lots of children, no problem.

01:02:57.880 --> 01:03:00.560
And we don’t have divorces either.

01:03:00.560 --> 01:03:08.880
So you must understand your own position –
specially ladies in the West.

01:03:08.880 --> 01:03:10.200
There is a trick of the trade.

01:03:10.200 --> 01:03:14.160
And if they don’t know the trick of the trade
they can never be successful in marriage.

01:03:14.160 --> 01:03:17.280
Don’t try to be men.
A man cannot marry a man.

01:03:17.280 --> 01:03:25.760
Of course, in these days (Laughter)
– but we are not like that.

01:03:26.480 --> 01:03:30.200
You have to be ladies
and you have to be gentlemen

01:03:30.200 --> 01:03:32.000
and that’s how the marriages take place.

01:03:32.000 --> 01:03:37.120
And that’s how it’s all right –
and not to quarrel, not to fight.

01:03:37.120 --> 01:03:41.200
But to love each other,
to understand each other in the same love,

01:03:41.200 --> 01:03:46.760
to feel their love. It’s the best thing,
if you know that your love is the highest thing,

01:03:46.760 --> 01:03:51.360
I think. For Me that’s the highest
and makes you so nice and happy,

01:03:51.360 --> 01:03:55.720
because even to love someone,
another person doesn’t love you a little bit

01:03:56.280 --> 01:04:00.200
you cannot get the reflection of your love.

01:04:00.200 --> 01:04:04.000
But when you see the other person
also loves you then it’s done.

01:04:04.000 --> 01:04:10.996
So it’s a nice way of learning
how to have a private life of love.

01:04:10.996 --> 01:04:12.640
But it’s private.

01:04:12.640 --> 01:04:18.760
It’s not public on the street,
in the airport or anywhere. It’s very private.

01:04:18.760 --> 01:04:22.080
The more private you make it the better it is.

01:04:22.080 --> 01:04:27.280
And the more you try to express it outside
it’s going to be dangerous, very dangerous.

01:04:27.280 --> 01:04:30.520
I have told you many a times that people
who are kissing on the escalator

01:04:30.520 --> 01:04:35.920
are going for their divorce.

01:04:35.920 --> 01:04:40.560
We are deep people and deeply we should love
and deeply we should understand life.

01:04:40.560 --> 01:04:49.222
We should not waste ourselves
in nonsensical analysis – all right?

01:04:49.222 --> 01:04:49.240
May God bless you!

01:04:49.240 --> 01:04:55.640
So for all those who are getting married
we must give them a hand.&nbsp;&nbsp;

01:05:18.440 --> 01:05:18.520
(Applause)

01:05:26.000 --> 01:05:42.320
All right.&nbsp;&nbsp;

01:07:14.600 --> 01:07:16.880
May God bless you all!

01:07:16.880 --> 01:07:19.240
I am always with you.
You are always with Me.

01:07:19.800 --> 01:07:24.280
I know, you are always with Me.
I know that but still you know

01:07:24.280 --> 01:07:28.920
sometimes you feel concerned.
Look after yourself.

01:07:28.920 --> 01:07:43.280
Don’t go out in the fog. (Laughter)

01:07:43.280 --> 01:07:47.000
And meditate, meditate – that you forget.

01:07:47.000 --> 01:07:49.596
Every time I need not tell you,
every time need not tell you.

01:07:49.596 --> 01:07:51.400
You must meditate both the times.

01:07:51.400 --> 01:07:55.640
Let the children also meditate
otherwise they’ll become difficult children.

01:07:55.640 --> 01:07:58.800
Force them to meditate.
They must meditate.

01:07:58.800 --> 01:08:02.702
If the children don’t meditate
they will have trouble,

01:08:02.702 --> 01:08:04.240
they will be very troublesome children.

01:08:04.240 --> 01:08:52.840
So try to make them meditate, all right?
May God&nbsp;&nbsp;

01:08:52.840 --> 01:08:54.400
bless you

